item.title: Inspecting Control Mechanics using T-Tests on Fallout New Vegas
item.description: The plot of the sequel of Fallout 3 takes context in the year 2281, 4 years after the first escape from Vault 101, within a post-apocalyptic world after the Great War. This RPG has an open world inspired by cities such as Nevada, California, Arizona, and Utah, allowing users to have a large number of places to explore and a world with NPCs to interact with, ideal for developing behavioral and exploratory analysis.
